{"id": 2864, "genre": 1000, "title": "聊天中的哪些行为会让你觉得敷衍？", "description": "向对方发射一个笑话后，对方回复了含哈量严重不足的：「哈哈哈」。（图片来源：视觉中国）", "record_count": 16987, "comment_count": 41, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2019032516533598KpJVgSuGtln3sr.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-28T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5579, "title": "聊天中的哪些行为会让你觉得敷衍？", "content": "聊天中的哪些行为让你觉得敷衍？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 335422, "content": "赞同敷衍，“好吧”、“你说的都对”、“666”", "image": "img/option/option/20190325165933WGswYITyN6E1A2li.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335429, "content": "表情敷衍，每句话都用表情包/表情回复：）", "image": "img/option/option/20190325170326Dt8qEKjcaP4ViAde.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335436, "content": "哈哈敷衍，含哈量严重不足，哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/20190325170830FZK34ofn20h5iNBm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335439, "content": "晚安敷衍，说了要睡觉了后又发了一条动态", "image": "img/option/option/20190325171042YGVrqhORJHs5nj9B.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335448, "content": "标点符号敷衍，用标点符号表示已阅，，/……/。。。", "image": "img/option/option/201903251743134xzg9eBNHQuIWRlS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335451, "content": "眼神敷衍，面对面聊天的时候没有眼神交流", "image": "img/option/option/2019032517245273q2jkxLMZelGzOE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335456, "content": "稍后回复敷衍，于是等了一周都还没回复", "image": "img/option/option/20190325172823N3LqHbr9KSuEGI5T.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335459, "content": "安慰敷衍，“多喝热水”、“抱抱”", "image": "img/option/option/20190325173507xD1UnIGv2Y3TSaJw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335463, "content": "我觉得都是人之常情，没感觉敷衍", "image": "img/option/option/20190325173658R1AaXgeOTJG4BUIt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}